attr_labels.identifier: An identifier that applies to this person in this role.
attr_labels.qualification.period: Period during which the qualification is valid.
attr_labels.address: Address(es) of the practitioner that are not role specific (typically home address). Work addresses are not typically entered in this property as they are usually role dependent.
attr_labels.gender: Administrative Gender - the gender that the person is considered to have for administration and record keeping purposes.
attr_labels.active: Whether this practitioner's record is in active use.
attr_labels.birthDate: The date of birth for the practitioner.
attr_labels.qualification.issuer: Organization that regulates and issues the qualification.
attr_labels.qualification.identifier: An identifier that applies to this person's qualification in this role.
attr_labels.qualification: The official certifications, training, and licenses that authorize or otherwise pertain to the provision of care by the practitioner.  For example, a medical license issued by a medical board authorizing the practitioner to practice medicine within a certian locality.
attr_labels.name: The name(s) associated with the practitioner.
attr_labels.telecom: A contact detail for the practitioner, e.g. a telephone number or an email address.
attr_labels.communication: A language the practitioner can use in patient communication.
